						<div class="postbody">Hi!<br /><br />I just got around to test the new feature. Its great! The one thing I would tweak is that I would highlight tiles/att changes regardless of whether the data has actually changed or not. When debugging scrolling (for example) you will often rewrite the same data (imagine a blue sky in mario), but you still want to know you did it correctly. The PPU is kind of a write-only thing for most developers.<br /><br />-Mat</div>

